  "description": "Artisan Morphus table (Dark Designs (WB6), pp. 26-27). Artistic Nightbane and those who share a great appreciation for art may find their Morphus forms reflect creative identity through painterly, sculptural, literary, costume, metalwork, musical, or body-art features (WB6 pp. 26-27).",
  "entries": [
    {
      "id": "artisan_paint_palette",
      "name": "Paint Palette",
      "tableCategory": "Artisan",
      "gameSystems": [
        "nightbane"
      ],
      "sources": [
        {
          "gameSystem": "nightbane",
          "reference": "Dark Designs (WB6)",
          "pageNumber": 26
        }
      ],
      "description": "Attached to the forearm is a wide board containing a number of daubs of different colored paints that never run out. Accompanied by a quiver-like container of paintbrushes hanging from a belt or shoulder-strap.",
      "statModifiers": {
        "perception": {
          "flat": 2
        },
